<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿlmny yạ rb ṭryqk .. fạ̉slk fy ḥqk
 wḥd qlby lkẖwf ạsmk .. (wlạ tḥjb ʿny wjhk)2
 ạlqrạr- (ydạk ṣnʿtny wkwnty .. wbạlḥnạn dạỷmaⁿạ ạ̉ḥạṭtny)2
 fhmny fạ̉tʿlm wṣạyạk .. wạ̉nṭlq lạ̉ḥqq nwạyạk
 2- sydy yạ lḥn lḥn ạlslạm .. yạ bạry kl ạlạ̉nạm
 yạ mn tḥml kl ạlậlạm .. (qwnạ wqdnạ llạ̉mạm)2</lyrics>
